title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Daily 3' game
maintext:
CHARLESTON, W.Va. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the West Virginia Lottery’s “Daily 3” game were:
5-5-9
(five, five, nine)
